summary: Replaces Karliah\'s violet eyes with proper dunmer eyes.
descriptionHtml:
Did a quick search and couldn\'t find anything, so I made it myself.

Replaces Karliah\'s eyes with a correct Dunmer eye colour.

She was already enough of a Mary Sue after the retcons of some of the longest standing elder scrolls lore without being exempt from having red eyes like every other Dunmer.

Not compatible with Ethereal Elven Overhaul
Not compatible with any other mod that modifies Karliah
author: SF Legend
